{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/94180", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/94180/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/94180/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/94180/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/94180", "id": 1144981226, "node_id": "I_kwDOAAsO6M5EPwbq", "number": 94180, "title": "rustdoc: macro calls in alias (stringify!)", "user": {"login": "ranfdev", "id": 23294184, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIzMjk0MTg0", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/23294184?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev", "html_url": "https://github.com/ranfdev", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ranfdev/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 203738, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyMDM3Mzg=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/T-rustdoc", "name": "T-rustdoc", "color": "bfd4f2", "default": false, "description": "Relevant to the rustdoc team, which will review and decide on the PR/issue."}], "state": "open", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 1, "created_at": "2022-02-20T10:35:59Z", "updated_at": "2023-01-28T09:45:51Z", "closed_at": null, "author_association": "NONE", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "When working with ffi, sometimes I need to alias the rust function to the foreign one.\r\n```rust\r\n#[doc(alias = \"ffi_fun\")]\r\nfn myfun() {\r\n  // ...\r\n  ffi_fun()\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\nSince I need to wrap many foreign functions, I use a macro (created with macro_rules) which looks roughly like this:\r\n```rust\r\n#[doc(alias = stringify!($ffi_fun))]\r\nfn $fun() {\r\n  // ...\r\n  $ffi_fun()\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n`stringify!`, `concat!` and other similar macros are really useful to generate the alias. It would be nice being able to use them", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/94180/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/94180/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}